TradeSage is an AI-driven financial intelligence platform that utilizes Multi-Agent Systems and Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) to provide real-time market insights. By combining autonomous agents with live data from sources like Yahoo Finance, it transforms raw market signals into actionable trading strategies through a conversational interface.

Key Technical Highlights
Multi-Agent Architecture: Features specialized ADK (Agent Development Kit) agents, including a Synthesis Agent for data processing and a Chat Agent for user interaction.

RAG Implementation: Uses Retrieval-Augmented Generation to ground AI responses in actual financial documents and live market data.

Cloud-Native Stack: Built with Python and JavaScript, containerized via Docker, and designed for seamless deployment on Google Cloud Platform (GCP) using Cloud Run and Cloud SQL.

Live Data Integration: Built-in hooks for real-time financial data fetching and automated simulation testing.
